<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.5">
<l>eṅṅaṉē yuyvar tāṉavar niṉaintā liraṇiya ṉilaṅkupū ṇakalam</l>
<l>poṅkuveṅ kuruti poṉmalai piḷantu poḻitaru maruviyot tiḻiya</l>
<l>veṅkaṇvā ḷeyiṟṟōr veḷḷimā vilaṅkal viṇṇuṟak kaṉalviḻit teḻunta</l>
<l>taṅṅaṉē yokka variyuru vāṉā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How do the Dānavas live if [they] think [about it]?</l>
<l rend="indent">The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam</l>
<l>Is the one who appeared in a lion form, with sharp fangs and burning eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">glaring with fire to reach the heavens,</l>
<l>So he resembled a great silver mountain rising,</l>
<l rend="indent">as bubbling, hot blood descended like a cascade which gushed freely,</l>
<l>Having split Hiraṇya’s gold mountain[-like] chest with shining jewels.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
